genresAdvancedInfo.name: umea indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Umea indie is a subgenre of indie rock that originated in the city of Umea, Sweden. It is characterized by its lo-fi production, introspective lyrics, and melodic guitar riffs. The genre has a DIY ethos and often features artists who are part of the local music scene in Umea. Umea indie bands often experiment with different genres, incorporating elements of punk, folk, and shoegaze into their music.
